		<p>Hryciuk Gallinger and its predecessor firms, has been 
			providing accounting and consulting services since 1977. We have a strong 
			belief in the community in which we operate and adhere to ethical business 
			practices and values.</p>
		<p>Bruce Hryciuk FCGA is the founding member of the firm and has 
			been active in the partnership since 1977. Donna Gallinger CGA joined the firm 
			in 1986 and, after having attained her designation, became a partner in 1995.</p>
		<p>Hryciuk Gallinger offers a complete range of accounting, 
			auditing, taxation and consulting services including:</p>

		<p class="BrochSubTitle">Accounting Services</p>
			<ul>
			
				<li>
					Computerized bookkeeping on a monthly, quarterly or annual basis</li><li>
					Preparation of payrolls and related statutory filings</li><li>Preparation of 
					T4, 15 and Subcontractor reports</li><li>Completion and filing of GST, PSI, WCB 
					and payroll source deduction remittances</li><li>Preparation of computer 
					generated interim financial statements</li><li>Preparation of year end review 
					engagement financial statements</li><li>Preparation of financing applications 
					and business plans</li><li>
					Preparation of forecasts and projections including cash flow analysis</li></ul>
		
		<p class="BrochSubTitle">Auditing Services</p>
        <ul>
				<li>
					Statutory audits of lawyer’s trust accounts</li><li>Statutory audits of real 
					estate trust accounts</li><li>Audits of not for profit enterprises</li><li>Audits 
					of profit oriented enterprises</li><li>Specialized audits for bonding, internal 
					control or forensic purposes</li></ul>
		
		<p class="BrochSubTitle">Taxation Services</p>
    <ul>
				<li>
					Preparation of TI personal income tax returns</li><li>Preparation of T2 
					corporation income tax returns and related GIFI schedules</li><li>Preparation 
					of T3 trust and estate tax returns including
					<ul>
						<li>
							Testamentary trusts</li><li>Family trusts</li><li>lnter-vivos trusts</li><li>Tax 
							planning services for corporations and individuals</li></ul>
				</li>
			</ul>
	
		<p class="BrochSubTitle">Consulting Services</></p>
		<ul>
				<li>
					Business commencement and set up</li><li>Income tax planning</li><li>Estate 
					planning</li><li>Management information systems</li><li>Computer applications 
					and implementation</li><li>Hands-on computer set up and training in accounting 
					and payroll software</li><li>Business acquisition and sale — investigations and 
					advice</li><li>Business operational advice
				</li>
			</ul>
		
		<p class="SmallText">The partners and staff of Hryciuk Gallinger are committed to 
			providing professional and friendly service that responds to your requirements 
			and needs. Our goal is to help you succeed in your business or personal affairs 
			by providing useful and timely advice and service.</p>
    
