                    <h4>Tax Season</h4>
                    <p>
                        Tax season is here and to help you prepare for document submission you can download our Personal Tax Information form here from our resources page: <a href="/documents/pti.pdf" target="_blank">Personal Tax Information Form</a></p>
                    <hr style="border-style: dashed" width="80%" />
                    <h4>Returning to PST</h4>
                    <p>
                        British Columbia’s provincial sales tax (PST) will be re-implemented effective April 1, 2013 at a general tax rate of seven per cent.
                        Read more here: <a href="http://www.pstinbc.ca">Click here for more about returning to PST</a></p>
                    <hr style="border-style: dashed" width="80%" />
                    <h4>Penny Discontinued</h4>
                    <p>The Royal Canadian Mint officially discontinued distribution of the penny on Feb 4, 2013, causing businesses to round the cost when customers pay with cash. <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Penny_(Canadian_coin)">Click here for more about the penny</a></p>
